   <body>
      <p>Every time you log in, you are navigated to the <ph href="../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/> Home page. </p>
      <p>In the application, the modules and information available to you are based on the following factors:<ul>
            <li>Roles assigned to you</li>
            <li>Projects to which you are invited</li>
            <li>Current workflow status of the form</li>
         </ul>
      </p>
      <p>The high-level modules, elements, and features available in <ph href="../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/> User Interface (UI) is illustrated in the following figure:</p>
      <p>
         <fig>
            <title>Mind Home Page<image href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/Mind_Home_Page.jpg"
                      placement="inline"/>
            </title>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>The UI of <ph href="../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/> contains various elements that are described as follows:</p>
      <p>
         <table colsep="1" rowsep="1">
            <tgroup cols="3">
               <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="10%"/>
               <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="20%"/>
               <colspec colname="c3" colnum="3" colwidth="70%"/>
               <thead>
                  <row>
                     <entry>Number</entry>
                     <entry>Item</entry>
                     <entry>Description</entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 1 </entry>
                     <entry>Profile Menu </entry>
                     <entry>View your profile, change your application password, log out, access the application Online Help, and view the application version information.<p>Click your initials to view the options.</p>
                        <p>
                           <image width="4cm"
                                  href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/UI-Profile.jpg"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Profile Menu</alt>
                           </image>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>2 </entry>
                     <entry>Favorites </entry>
                     <entry>Bookmark frequently used pages for easy and quick access from anywhere in the application. <p>For information on accessing and managing your favorites, refer to <xref href="../../Common_Application_Features/Standard_Form_Functions/Bookmarking/BookmarkFavs.xml">Managing Favorites</xref>.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>3 </entry>
                     <entry>Page navigation trail/Breadcrumbs </entry>
                     <entry>The trail of page navigation links is displayed to track your location within the application. <p>Click a link to open the page.</p>
                        <p>
                           <image width="450"
                                  href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/UI-Breadcrumbs.png"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Breadcrumb</alt>
                           </image>
                        </p>
                        <p>Expand the breadcrumb trail to access the whole trail.</p>
                        <p>
                           <image width="450"
                                  href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/UI-CompleteBCTrail.png"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Breadcrumbs Trail</alt>
                           </image>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 4 </entry>
                     <entry>Form finder </entry>
                     <entry>Type the name of the form, or part of the form name to easily find the form in the navigation pane. <p>
                           <image width="4cm"
                                  href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/Form_Finder.jpg"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Form Finder - Search Menu</alt>
                           </image>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 5 </entry>
                     <entry>Module Name </entry>
                     <entry>Displays the name of the module you are currently in.</entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 6 </entry>
                     <entry>Module Menu </entry>
                     <entry>Buttons to access the various modules of <ph href="../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/>. </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 7 </entry>
                     <entry>Toggle button </entry>
                     <entry>Button to show, hide, and re-size application panes. <p>Docking the left pane provides more space to view information in the right pane.</p>
                        <p>Click <image href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/UI-NavToggle1.jpg"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Toggle Close</alt>
                           </image> to hide the left navigation pane.</p>
                        <p>Click <image href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/UI-NavToggle2.jpg"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Toggle Open</alt>
                           </image> to view the left navigation pane.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 8 </entry>
                     <entry>Left navigation pane </entry>
                     <entry>Links to the forms  available in the module. </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 9 </entry>
                     <entry>Right action pane </entry>
                     <entry>Displays the work area for forms and modules. </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 10 </entry>
                     <entry>Loading bar </entry>
                     <entry>Displays in motion when page load is in progress. </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry> 11 </entry>
                     <entry>Toggle button </entry>
                     <entry>Button to show the names of the modules in <ph href="../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/>. <p>Click the toggle button <image href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/UI-ModToggle1.jpg"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Toggle button</alt>
                           </image> to view the module names.</p>
                        <p>
                           <image width="4cm"
                                  href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/Toggle_Button.jpg"
                                  placement="inline"/>
                        </p>
                        <p>Click the toggle button <image href="../../Mind/Getting_Started/Screenshots/UI-ModToggle2.jpg"
                                  placement="inline">
                              <alt>Close Side Navigation Panel</alt>
                           </image> to hide the module names.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
